name: Crash Landed (itch) (Clenched22)
description: This is my very first game created within a game class. This game is about a girl named Ellen. Now I decided to picture it as her have a crash landing on this random world with many different habitats. I see her going through a struggle to stay alive and get to the end to survive this world. Please enjoy. Also, please go easy on me as it's all made out of a free gamekit.
